<i>noun</i>: 참회 [참회/참훼], 자책 [자책] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>참회 [참회/참훼]</dt><br>
<dd>repentance; remorse; self-reproach</dd><br>
<dd>잘못을 깨닫고 부끄럽게 생각하여 뉘우침.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of realizing one's shameful wrongdoings and regretting them.</dd><br>
<dt>자책 [자책]</dt><br>
<dd>self-reproach</dd><br>
<dd>스스로 잘못했다고 생각하여 자신을 꾸짖고 나무람.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of scolding and rebuking oneself for one's own wrongdoing.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>